COMMON COMMANDS


Docker commands:

#Compose down (stop conatiners) - build again - compose up (compose again):
docker-compose down && docker-compose build && docker-compose up -d

#Check the logs of a specific container:
d logs --tail 50 --follow --timestamps <ID>

#Enter the sh of a container:
docker exec -it <ID>  sh



Create an SSL Certificate and Key:
sudo openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -keyout flask-app-key.pem -out flask-app-cert.crt -sha256 -days 3650 -nodes -subj "/C=XX/ST=StateName/L=CityName/O=CompanyName/OU=CompanySectionName/CN=CommonNameOrHostname"
